-- EUROPE RESEARCH ROUNDUP-BT Group, Bank Pekao, Fiat Chrysler 
-- 
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 02:49AM EDT
-- None



Oct 31 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several European companies, including Bank Pekao and BT Group, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Oil & Gas: SocGen cuts Rockhopper Exploration <RKH.L> to sell [ID:nWNAB053AP]  * Polish Banks: SocGen cuts Bank Pekao <PEO.WA> to sell [ID:nWNAB053AN]   * BT Group <BT.L>: S&P Capital IQ cuts to sell from hold * Fiat Chrysler <FCHA.MI>: Morgan Stanley starts with overweight ratingFollowing is a summary of research actions on European companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Africa Oil <AOIC.ST>: SocGen cuts price target to Sek 40 from Sek 46; rating buy * Alcatel Lucent <ALUA.PA>: S&P Capital IQ raises target to 2.50 from 2.25 euros; hold * Bank Zachodni WBK <BZW.WA>: SocGen cuts price target to Pln 412 from Pln 421; rating hold * Bank Pekao <PEO.WA>: SocGen cuts to sell from hold * Bank Pekao <PEO.WA>: SocGen cuts price target to Pln 160 from Pln 176 * Bayer AG <BAYGn.DE>: S&P Capital IQ raises to buy from hold * BE Semiconductor <BESI.AS>: Canaccord Genuity raises target to 18 from 17 euros; buy * BT Group <BT.L>: S&P Capital IQ cuts to sell from hold * Cairn Energy <CNE.L>: SocGen cuts price target to 170p from 200p; rating hold * Fiat Chrysler <FCHA.MI>: Morgan Stanley starts with overweight rating * Fiat Chrysler <FCHA.MI>: Morgan Stanley starts with price target 13 euros * Kuka AG <KU2G.DE>: DZ Bank raises target to 38.00 euros from 34.00 euros; rating sell * Linde <LING.DE>: S&P Capital IQ cuts to sell from hold * Lundin Petroleum <LUPE.ST>: SocGen cuts price target to Sek 127 from Sek 142; rating hold * Maurel & Prom <MAUP.PA>: SocGen cuts price target to 13.2 euros from 14 euros; rating buy * Megafon <MFONq.L>: Citi Research cuts price target to $25.45 from $30.20; rating neutral * Ophir Energy <OPHR.L>: SocGen cuts price target to 218p from 230p; rating hold * Peugeot <PEUP.PA>: Exane BNP Paribas cuts target by 3 pct to 13.7 euros; rating outperform * PKO Bank Polski <PKO.WA>: SocGen cuts price target to Pln 38 from Pln 40; rating hold * Premier Oil <PMO.L>: SocGen cuts price target to 293p from 350p; rating hold * Renault <RENA.PA>: Exane BNP Paribas cuts target by 3 pct to 68 euros; rating neutral * Rockhopper Exploration <RKH.L>: SocGen cuts to sell from hold * RPS Group Plc <RPS.L>: Jefferies cuts price target to 300p from 320p; rating buy * Smith & Nephew <SN.L>: Barclays raises target price to 1140p from 1120p; rating overweight * Tullow Oil Plc <TLW.L>: SocGen cuts price target to 690p from 700p; rating buy